OL,3,CPSNI officers issued with advice after
OL,4,C'degrading comments'
OL,6,FThree police officers have been issued
OL,7,Fwith advice and a fourth subject with
OL,8,Fmeasures to improve conduct following
OL,9,F"degrading and inappropriate
OL,10,Fcomments", the office of the Police
OL,11,FOmbudsman has said.
OL,13,FIt comes after an investigation by the
OL,14,Fwatchdog found officers used degrading
OL,15,Flanguage about a man and his partner,
OL,16,Fand mishandled evidence after a mobile
OL,17,Fphone was seized during his arrest.
OL,19,FThree officers were issued with advice
OL,20,Fto improve their conduct as well as
OL,21,Ftheir handling of property.
