OL,6,FIn a statement, the Police Ombudsman's
OL,7,FOffice said it recommended the PSNI
OL,8,Fshould hold misconduct meetings with
OL,9,Fall four officers.
OL,11,FThis was not accepted by the PSNI's
OL,12,FProfessional Standards Department,
OL,13,Fwhich decided instead to hold a
OL,14,Fmisconduct meeting with one officer
OL,15,Fand offer advice to the others.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
