OL,6,FIt also said officers had been unaware
OL,7,Fthe man's phone had been recording
OL,8,Faudio from before his arrest and
OL,9,Fthroughout his time in police custody,
OL,10,Fand that the recording included
OL,11,Fseveral concerning comments and
OL,12,Frevealed issues with how officers had
OL,13,Fdealt with the phone.
