OL,4,C'degrading comments'
OL,6,FThe officer who made the initial
OL,7,Fcomment about damaging the phone was
OL,8,Finterviewed under criminal caution on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of attempting, or
OL,10,Fencouraging someone else, to break the
OL,11,Fdevice.
OL,13,FA file was submitted to the Public
OL,14,FProsecution Service (PPS), which
OL,15,Fdirected that the officer would not be
OL,16,Fprosecuted.
