OL,3,CPSNI officers issued with advice after
OL,4,C'degrading comments'
OL,6,F"While these comments were made by
OL,7,Fpolice officers outside of a public
OL,8,Fsetting, they nonetheless reflect
OL,9,Fattitudes and behaviours that are
OL,10,Fentirely unacceptable," he said.
OL,12,F"It is particularly concerning that
OL,13,Fsuch degrading remarks were directed
OL,14,Ftowards a woman reporting to be a
OL,15,Fvictim of domestic abuse.
OL,17,F"This serves as a reminder that police
OL,18,Fofficers should always act with
OL,19,Fcompassion, professionalism and
OL,20,Fintegrity."
