OL,3,CPSNI officers issued with advice after
OL,4,C'degrading comments'
OL,6,FHe added: "This is another case in
OL,7,Fwhich we identified that police
OL,8,Fofficers failed to deal appropriately
OL,9,Fwith an electronic device.
OL,11,F"The protection of personal data and
OL,12,Fthe preservation of potential digital
OL,13,Fevidence is of critical importance yet
OL,14,Fwe have a number of cases involving
OL,15,Fconcerns that police procedures
OL,16,Fgoverning this area are not being
OL,17,Ffollowed."
