OL,3,CPSNI officers issued with advice after
OL,4,C'degrading comments'
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Julie Mullan,
OL,7,Ffrom the PSNI's Professional Standards
OL,8,FDepartment, said it acknowledges the
OL,9,Ffindings of the report.
OL,11,FShe said: "The Police Service of
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland and the public expect
OL,13,Fpolice officers to investigate
OL,14,Fincidents fully, fairly and
OL,15,Fprofessionally.
OL,17,F"Where it is perceived that conduct
OL,18,Ffalls short of these high standards,
OL,19,Fit is right that officers should face
OL,20,Fan impartial, thorough inquiry by the
OL,21,FPolice Ombudsman's office.
