OL,3,CPSNI officers issued with advice after
OL,4,C'degrading comments'
OL,6,F"As a result of the investigation,
OL,7,Fthree police officers have been issued
OL,8,Fwith advice to improve their conduct
OL,9,Fwhile a fourth officer was subject to
OL,10,Fmeasures designed to improve
OL,11,Fperformance.
OL,13,F"While in this instance the conduct of
OL,14,Fthe officers fell short of the
OL,15,Fstandards that we have set, it is not
OL,16,Frepresentative of the excellent work
OL,17,Fpolice officers carry out across
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland on a daily basis as
OL,19,Fwe strive to keep people safe."
